item.title: std.tf
item.description: module std.tf The standard module contains basic functions for general computing tasks. library core The core library contains utility functions to process values at a basic level. id (any x) -> any Identity function. Returns x. > core.id("foo") "foo" > core.id({:a "b"}) { :a "b" } > core.id(nil) nil inspect (x) -> string Returns a string representation of x. If x is a function the string 'function' is returned.
